<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Rung</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-01-19 10:29:38</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I have to TOATLLY disagree with your comment on the spawn rate of 1 in 50. The Knight ALWAYS spawns about once an hour. As far as the Knight actually having the tunic, well, thats about 1 out of about 6 Knights you kill. So the odds are not that bad. If you go to Unrest and put your time in, you will get one as I did. Of course you have to win the lotto too. :-)  Kid b4 me rolled a 97 and I rolled a 99. hee hee</font></td></tr></table>
