<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Kinter</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-02-07 02:15:13</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Just to let you know:  we might have been INCREDIBLY unlucky, but we had a group camping the Knight room for about 20 hours this weekend.  Grand total, we got 0 (ZERO) BS Tunics.  We did get about four or five mantles, a dozen thick leather aprons (from the barkeep downstairs), four opalline earrings (also from the barkeep), five savant's caps (from the magi down the hall), and one ivory bracelet (from the reanimated hand down the hall in the other direction).<BR>
<BR>
Frankly, I don't know why BS Tunics sell for so LITTLE.  I have owned three now, and I'm always happiest when I have one; I think they are the best chest piece a Cleric can have, this side of Guk.  And despite having camped the Knight room for a rather long length of time, I have NEVER seen one drop from the Knight itself.</font></td></tr></table>
