<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Tordor</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-06-19 19:02:07</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>This is a great item and the only reason it sell so cheap is because it drops consistantly and it is a common camp. I have gotten several of them and when I created a shaman this was one of the first items that I looked for.  The walls are thin in Unrest and the bar mobs will run upstairs if it's not camped and things can get hairy.  The other tip is to jump right on the festering hags as they pop with dual wield to prevent them from casting as much. If all goes bad you can jump out the window and run to the zone but be sure to have the courtesy to let everyone know with a /shout</font></td></tr></table>
