<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>This is a very nice piece of armour for a cleric. Just don't wear it with bronze leggings and arms. It clashes horribly. The same goes for banded. Do yourself a favour and get yourself some Blackened or Ringmail legs and arms.</font></td></tr></table>
